dc_title_s: Public Lands Survey System, Townships and Ranges in the United States, 2011
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the Public Land Survey System data at the township level.This layer can be used to identify townships and ranges within the Public Land Survey System. This dataset is intended to assist users in locating and analyzing United States oil and gas field data and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
